---
title: Thai Eggplant & Broccoli Yellow Curry with Roasted Peanuts
description: Rich, creamy and lightly spiced, Thai yellow curry is universally popular. Add cubes of roasted eggplant, tender-crisp broccoli and Asian greens to make a delicious veggie curry that'll put a smile on everyone's dial.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-eggplant-broccoli-yellow-curry-eeaa7b2c.jpg
